      "content": "\"working with flaws\" sounds like I'd just be managing my own misery forever. i've spent years doing that. it just feels like i'm dragging around a corpse. sometimes it feels like the most honest thing i could do is just stop fighting it and accept that i'm just... finished. like, what if the \"broken\" part is just the permanent reality of who i am?",
